>https://youtu.be/95N9GKZ7zqU?t=6m20s</a>"},{"pid":"1a2235b0e34d3a501b9ff47796784b3b57ad06c9","tid":327202,"uid":19141,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會阻礙衛星航行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講射上太空應該都係射出地球個重力場<br />\n唔會阻到現有衛星同增加地球既太空垃圾"},{"pid":"45b0179f028b051dbf2272a7e2626094202cbf04","tid":327202,"uid":76355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我有諗過海平面上升<br />\n運d水去荒漠化地區is ok 👨🏻&zwj;🏫</blockquote><br />\n呢個topic幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴打分析下有冇可能實行到？</blockquote><br />\n要運幾多轉先升到1mm？<br />\n運輸過程出啲溫室氣體都可能又夠升返個海平面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80670ed18ea05621a895ca3f2cff8d9a8bd07c8","tid":327202,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"我想上太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0c594bba7564980ed6f85cb64a016425ed2918","tid":327202,"uid":61960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:20:36.000Z","msg":"以小弟有限既知識，係因為地心吸力既關係，除非你d垃圾超出地球既吸力範圍外，唔係既話d垃圾都會圍住個地球轉。而目前圍住地球轉既都有太空垃圾，隕石碎片等等，全部都高速旋轉緊。而依個問題都會越嚟越嚴重，太多垃圾圍住地球會破壞太空站望遠鏡衛星。而將垃圾扔出範圍外需要好多錢，當務之急係解決太空垃圾先。（應該係<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"0e92384c35f0d30a409c13005bc1c2f55049c646","tid":327202,"uid":86988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:33:24.000Z","msg":"如果可以搞咁大，做乜唔直接起垃圾焚化爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.可以發電<br />\n2.低土地佔用面積 細過堆填區<br />\n3.處理垃圾速度快<br />\n4.可以令垃圾面積變為原本嘅10%或以下<br />\n5.副產物又多用途<br />\netc."},{"pid":"2f4bde16adbb142a045867944d7c42d6fa865ca0","tid":327202,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果可以搞咁大，做乜唔直接起垃圾焚化爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.可以發電<br />\n2.低土地佔用面積 細過堆填區<br />\n3.處理垃圾速度快<br />\n4.可以令垃圾面積變為原本嘅10%或以下<br />\n5.副產物又多用途<br />\netc.</blockquote><br />\n污染呢？"},{"pid":"c0f524b8fce8bb299bfd3d2a8417932fbc4b628d","tid":327202,"uid":50165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:38:41.000Z","msg":"土星有土星環，地球都要有地球環"},{"pid":"7a1395ceaedcf45fad785502196d7b4fcd5fa597","tid":327202,"uid":74259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"樓豬有冇諗過整一隻飛船會產生幾多垃圾同污染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94c96efc1f97710253f7d1ad1d769c44a28f469","tid":327202,"uid":72730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:39:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果可以搞咁大，做乜唔直接起垃圾焚化爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.可以發電<br />\n2.低土地佔用面積 細過堆填區<br />\n3.處理垃圾速度快<br />\n4.可以令垃圾面積變為原本嘅10%或以下<br />\n5.副產物又多用途<br />\netc.</blockquote><br />\n污染呢？</blockquote><br />\n不如研究降低焚化既污染仲實際"},{"pid":"fb0b5b9fce26cd73f6448c75ff8c15f3a0f52de3","tid":327202,"uid":29489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"點解咁都講得出<br />\n樓主想上太空？"},{"pid":"fe2c336293e81eaf3bf334c321b1e3c489ded688","tid":327202,"uid":20164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:51:44.000Z","msg":"其實直接搵過火山<br />\n溶岩燒哂佢<br />\n又無剩餘物 唔知得唔得呢"},{"pid":"c63497a67c1b90b0d35a37848b9686764dd78832","tid":327202,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架仔發明d焚化爐好似好堅"},{"pid":"d9e93309fd253dcc98d83a6a598b068c1571c6dc","tid":327202,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬有冇諗過整一隻飛船會產生幾多垃圾同污染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲用飛船，所以你地真係無發明家嘅頭腦，太過frame死住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要低成本一定唔會用現有嘅方法囉，唔係點解要研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8469720a39fe3b72aac398d5b50a6a41c73e0c45","tid":327202,"uid":42374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:59:44.000Z","msg":"圍住地球已經夠多太空垃圾 <br />\n宜家研究緊點樣解決太空垃圾問題<br />\n避免將來影響地球<br />\n樓豬又話叫人研究扔多啲上去<br />\n做足功課先衝出黎柒啦基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e695243b0e3a9942cf27ad4e1905894d4ef3cba","tid":327202,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:00:17.000Z","msg":"軌道電梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64301a96aab6ad914d2fd91e4290509be2840121","tid":327202,"uid":42374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"but樓豬死左咪少咁件垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9eb1a02dc04489eebee627d42a6a8ff107853de","tid":327202,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圍住地球已經夠多太空垃圾 <br />\n宜家研究緊點樣解決太空垃圾問題<br />\n避免將來影響地球<br />\n樓豬又話叫人研究扔多啲上去<br />\n做足功課先衝出黎柒啦基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飛出地球嘅引力範圍囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無追post㗎垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cfb3c264be556dba2a854d5ac2909bfcbbbbeb","tid":327202,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:06:54.000Z","msg":"點解唔掉去宇宙盡頭？因為成本問題囉！"},{"pid":"d9edfa1773764c93a850cceff576edadbf4d8d37","tid":327202,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我有諗過海平面上升<br />\n運d水去荒漠化地區is ok 👨🏻&zwj;🏫</blockquote><br />\n呢個topic幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴打分析下有冇可能實行到？</blockquote><br />\n要運幾多轉先升到1mm？<br />\n運輸過程出啲溫室氣體都可能又夠升返個海平面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n科技會發展架CHING<br />\n以前由香港去歐洲都要幾個月<br />\n依家1日都唔洗"},{"pid":"218b2467795a5736c96464e03aaf815bebecb383","tid":327202,"uid":86988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果可以搞咁大，做乜唔直接起垃圾焚化爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.可以發電<br />\n2.低土地佔用面積 細過堆填區<br />\n3.處理垃圾速度快<br />\n4.可以令垃圾面積變為原本嘅10%或以下<br />\n5.副產物又多用途<br />\netc.</blockquote><br />\n污染呢？</blockquote><br />\n不如研究降低焚化既污染仲實際</blockquote><br />\n在一九九七年燃燒十一萬六千五百噸都市固體廢物時，共排出21-27克二噁英﹔但二零零七年燃燒一百萬噸都市固體廢物，排出的二噁英僅餘0.6克<br />\n<br />\n經呼吸直接攝取的二噁英只佔人體二噁英攝取量百分之二以下，不會對公眾健康造成不良影響。<br />\n<br />\n隨着焚化技術提升，例如攝氏850度以上的高溫燃燒室、空氣洗滌系統、獨立的活性碳灌注系統或觸媒式濾袋以有效破壞二噁英等，已大大減少二噁英、懸浮粒子和有機污染物等的形成<br />\n<br />\n不如下次Google下先好唔好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下下都要人喂到埋口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef532661c819bca312bf8a5305bd8a04dfb6da3c","tid":327202,"uid":36575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"樓主想太空旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff07b22fdeb88ab7b8ff2ad49cf4e70d28ae9007","tid":327202,"uid":3976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"咪有囉 中國射親上去果d都係垃圾黎"},{"pid":"34d602261734f6691c320352db4017a32b7f62b3","tid":327202,"uid":124323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:16:31.000Z","msg":"如果運，有無諗過要運幾多先解決到問題？幾十億人一日產生幾多垃圾？<br />\n<br />\n係唔係日日用地球資源將d垃圾射出地球引力？係搞都搞左現有太空垃圾先啦<br />\n<br />\n岩，無咪研究囉，研究都研究左隨意門先啦"},{"pid":"1ee20b1b719b2cac51